        <updateDate>2020-02-20T20:51:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ensuring Access to Direct Support Professionals Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows state Medicaid programs to cover certain home- and community-based services, self-directed personal assistance services, and home- and community-based attendant services that are provided in acute care hospitals. The bill specifies, among other criteria, that such services may not be duplicative of, or serve as a substitute for, necessary or obligatory hospital services. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
